# Trivy ignore file — suppress specific findings for the security scan.
# https://trivy.dev/latest/docs/configuration/filtering/#by-finding-ids
#
# One finding ID per line (CVE, secret rule ID, or misconfiguration ID),
# optionally with an expiry date, e.g.:
#   CVE-2023-1234 exp:2026-12-31
#
# Keep this file curated — every entry is a knowingly accepted risk.
